channel.title: Java INVOKE command
channel.description:
what we have: method name and desc method and class access flags (public/private/interface,static etc.)
Is it possible to determine INVOKE type from information given above? i.e. special, virtual, static, interface Or can anyone explain the difference between invokevirtual and invokeinterface?
